*C{{sup|7}}: C–E–G–B{{music|b}}
*C{{sup|7{{music|b}}5}}: C–E–G{{music|b}}–B{{music|b}}
*C{{sup|7{{music|#}}5}}: C–E–G{{music|#}}–B{{music|b}}
*(C{{music|halfdim}}{{sup|7}}: C–E{{music|b}}–G{{music|b}}–B{{music|b}})
*(Cm{{sup|7{{music|#}}5}}: C–E{{music|b}}–G{{music|#}}–B{{music|b}})
